## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not capture the full diversity of community influences across different cultural and social contexts. Additionally, the reliance on user-generated content from platforms like Quora and Brainly may introduce subjective biases. Further research with a broader range of academic sources could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.

